<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <title>IAFC</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="ct" content="<%= ct %>">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/watson-bootstrap-dark.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/banner.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
  <div class="row service-container">
    <div class="col-lg-12 service-header">
      <div class="row top-nav navbar-fixed-top">
        <div class="container"><a href="https://iafc-sid-app.mybluemix.net/" class="top-nav--logo-link"><h3 class="heading left">IAFC <span class="top-nav--logo-wdc">Fraud Detection Index</span></h3></a>
          <nav class="top-nav--nav">
            <li class="top-nav--nav-item"><a href="http://anshuchak063.wixsite.com/iafc" target="_blank">Website</a></li>
            <li class="top-nav--nav-item"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/IndiaAgainstFraudsandCorrupts/" target="_blank">Social Media</a></li>
            <li class="top-nav--nav-item"><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScCKC-DUNtt-jJjsszT1CHIOOq4llG0xeRBWA1sVzQ-mK4cXg/viewform?c=0&w=1" target="_blank">Report</a></li>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row header">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="avatar img-container col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-2 hidden-xs"><img src="/images/app.jpg" class="service-icon"></div>
          <div class="col-lg-10 col-md-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-12 dialog-description">
            <h1 style="font-size:50px;" class="service-title">India Against Frauds and Corrupts</h1>
            <p>Have you ever faced frauds and couldn't decide what to do at that point? Here we are, at IAFC, to help you along with other Indians fight corruption.Our services include collection and aggregation of data related to scams and frauds, simplification of filing of cases pertaining to illegal issues and using machine learning for swift detection of the same.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <h2>Try the service</h2>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12">
            <h3>Enter a phrase to check Fraud level</h3>
            <p class="help-block">Watch the Natural Language Classifier categorize your query. In this framework, the classifier is trained to determine whether the phrase is related to <em>fraud</em> or <em>genuine(N/F)</em>. The output includes
              the top classification and a confidence score.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-10 col-md-10 col-xs-8">
            <input placeholder="Enter your query or Try a sample phrase below" required="true" class="questionText form-control">
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-xs-4">
            <button class="btn btn-block ask-btn">Enter</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12">
            <h4>Sample Query</h4>
            <div class="example-questions"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-xs-12">
            <p class="help-block">The classifier often scores well with terms that it hasn't been trained on. In the sample questions, the words "lottery," "credit card," and "invest" are not part of the <a href="https://github.com/SidVader/Training-Data/blob/master/Fraud-Train.csv"
                target="_blank">training data</a>, yet the classifier correctly handles questions about them. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="height:300px;" class="col-lg-12">
        <div class="row">
          <h2>Results</h2></div>
        <div style="display:none" class="row loading">
          <div class="col-lg-12 col-xs-12 text-center"><img src="images/watson.gif" width="110px"></div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:none" class="results">
          <div class="well">
            <p>Team IAFC is <span class="confidence"></span> confident that the query submitted is talking about '<span class="classification"></span>'.</p>
            <p><strong>Classification: </strong><span class="classification"></span></p>
            <p><strong>Confidence: </strong><span class="confidence"></span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:none;" class="error">
          <h2>Error</h2>
          <div class="well">
            <div class="errorMsg"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/index.js"></script>

  <%if (ga) { %>
    <!-- Using Google Analytics -->
    <script>
      (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){
      (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),
      m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)
      })(window,document,'script','//www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga');

      ga('create', '<%= ga %>', 'auto');
      ga('send', 'pageview');
    </script>
  <% } %>
</body>

</html>
